@baseUrl = http://localhost:9876
@accessToken =
@refreshToken =
@clientId = my_client

### OIDC Discovery
GET {{baseUrl}}/.well-known/openid-configuration

### OIDC JWKS (public keys)
GET {{baseUrl}}/.well-known/jwks.json

###

### Sign up
POST {{baseUrl}}/sign-up
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=monkeyday&nickname=monkeyday&email=monkeyday@example.com&password=Secret!234

### Authorize (validate OIDC request)
GET {{baseUrl}}/authorize?response_type=code&client_id={{clientId}}&redirect_uri=http://localhost:3000/callback&scope=openid%20email%20profile&state=xyz&nonce=abc123

### Sign-in page (HTML)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sign-in
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### Get token (password grant)
POST {{baseUrl}}/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Forwarded-For: 1.2.3.4

{
  "grant_type": "password",
  "email": "monkeyday@example.com",
  "password": "Secret!234",
  "expire_secs": 86400
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.access_token);
  client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.refresh_token);
%}

### Refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grant_type": "refresh_token",
  "client_id": "{{clientId}}",
  "refresh_token": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.access_token);
  client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.refresh_token);
%}

###

### Create authorization code (OIDC login)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sign-in
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
X-Forwarded-For: 1.2.3.4

email=alice@example.com&password=secret1234&response_type=code&client_id={{clientId}}&redirect_uri=http://localhost:3000/callback&scope=openid+email+profile&state=xyz&nonce=abc123

### Exchange authorization code for tokens
POST {{baseUrl}}/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=authorization_code&code=<replace_with_code>&client_id={{clientId}}&redirect_uri=http://localhost:3000/callback

###

### Userinfo — OIDC standard endpoint (requires auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/userinfo
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get profile — alias (requires auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/oidc/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Revoke token (requires auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/oidc/revoke
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{accessToken}}",
  "token_type_hint": "access_token"
}

### Introspect token (requires auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/oidc/introspect
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{accessToken}}",
  "token_type_hint": "access_token"
}

### Forgot password (sends reset email; always returns 200 to avoid info leakage)
POST {{baseUrl}}/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "monkeyday@example.com"
}

### Reset password (consume the token from the reset email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "<token-from-reset-password-email>",
  "password": "NewSecret!234"
}

### Logout (OIDC end-session, redirects to post_logout_redirect_uri)
GET {{baseUrl}}/oidc/logout?id_token_hint={{accessToken}}&post_logout_redirect_uri=http://localhost:3000&state=xyz

### Update profile (requires auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v3/update-profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

user_id=<replace_with_user_id>&access_token={{accessToken}}&nickname=AliceUpdated&email=alice_new@example.com

### Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/debug/vars
